Package org.osmdroid.mapsforge

osmdroid addon that allows to use offline vector map-tiles (*.map files) using mapsforge lgpl library.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MapsForgeTileModuleProvider
    Adapted from code from here: https://github.com/MKergall/osmbonuspack, which is LGPL http://www.salidasoftware.com/how-to-render-mapsforge-tiles-in-osmdroid/
    MapsForgeTileProvider
    This lets you hook up multiple MapsForge files, it will render to the screen the first image that's available.
    MapsForgeTileSource
    Adapted from code from here: https://github.com/MKergall/osmbonuspack, which is LGPL http://www.salidasoftware.com/how-to-render-mapsforge-tiles-in-osmdroid/
